  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink100-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vāyiṉērtaṟ poruṭṭu mukam pukuvāṉ vēṇṭi iyaṟpaḻittuḻit talaimakaḷ iyaṟpaṭa
          moḻinta tiṟam talaimakaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink100">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>puṉalāṭu makaḷi riṭṭa voḷḷiḻai</l>
          <l>maṇalāṭu cimaiyat terumai kiḷaikkum</l>
          <l>yāṇa rūraṉ makaḷivaḷ</l>
          <l>pāṇar narampiṉu miṉkiḷa viyaḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> This girl is the daughter/ girl of the man from a fertile village,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the buffalo unearths, on dancing peaks of sand, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> the bright jewels buried by girls bathing in the flood – / </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the buffalo unearths the mountains [made] in play in the sand, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> [along with] the bright jewels buried by girls bathing in the flood –</l>
          <p/>
          <l> She whose speech is sweeter than the lute strings of bards.</l>


        </lg>

      </div>
